<br>
There's also a bit of a quandry about an NT passage that is most probably a later insertion used to support the Trinity concept. (1 John 5.7 - 5.8. See <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.bibletexts.com/kjv-tr.htm#3" target="top">this link</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> to see a discussion about Erasmus, the &quot;Textus Receptus&quot;, and the passage in question.)<br>
