<br>
In order to grow and progress, it was imperative that we gain a body of flesh and bone. So the earth was created to give us this opportunity.  Jesus was the first born Spirit Son of God and is part of the Godhead.  The Holy Ghost is another of our brothers and is part of the Godhead (kind of like a Presidency if you will with God as the President and Jesus and the Holy Ghost as His counsellors) acting with one purpose and the counsellors having the authority of God to act in His name to bring about His will.<br>
<br>
